Description: animator, constraint solver and model checker for B
 ProB is an animator, constraint solver and model checker for the B method. It
 also supports Event-B, CSP-M, TLA+ and Z, and can be used to systematically
 check a specification for a range of errors.
 .
 This package bundles the upstream SICStus Prolog based distribution and
 provides the Tcl/Tk user interface (prob) and the command-line tool (probcli).
